kupapa
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a Maori serving in the Crown's forces in the New Zealand Wars
Origin: Maori
Register: historical
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: cf. friendly
